.IX Item "-B2"
force \s-1ASCII\s0 after \s-1NL.\s0
.RE
.RS 4
.RE
.IP "\fB\-I\fR" 4
.IX Item "-I"
Replacing non iso\-2022\-jp char into a geta character
(substitute character in Japanese).
