To see \s-1ISO8859\-1\s0 (Latin\-1) \-l is necessary.
.RS 4
.IP "\fB\-mB\fR" 4
.IX Item "-mB"
Decode \s-1MIME\s0 base64 encoded stream. Remove header or other part before
